title: Spectate mode question
body: At the end of the spectate mode there is a screen much like at the end of the normal/draft modes. There above the stats of the players u can see 2 numbers.There aren't kills,gold,number of wins.. I don't know what they are. Does anyone know what those numbers represent?

replies.body: I'm not sure what you are referring to, unfortunately!  When you have a moment, toss a screenshot over here and we can take a look.  Let me know!

Here it is
[(https://www.google.com/search?site=&tbm=isch&source=hp&biw=1920&bih=979&q=lol+spectate+game+end+screen&oq=lol+spectate+game+end+screen&gs_l=img.3...2701.7258.0.7395.28.14.0.14.14.0.107.1134.13j1.14.0....0...1ac.1.64.img..0.18.1141...0j0i30k1j0i19k1j0i10i30i19k1j0i30i19k1j0i8i30i19k1j0i8i30k1j0i24k1.zWBZW9RdSwI#imgrc=aq2N-iR7lf5X0M%3A]
